==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: People don't know, and ghosts don't feel.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén bù zhī, gŭi bù júe

===Phrase===
'''[[人]][[不]][[知]]，[[鬼]][[不]][[觉]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Something that is so mysterious, that it cannot be known by humans or felt by ghosts.

===Alternate forms===
[[人]][[不]][[知]]，[[鬼]][[不]][[覺]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

